  "summary_text": "Asimi Silver Tear appears across 76 lore entries and carries 10 motif mentions spanning 2 unique motifs: Frost & Hoarfrost (9 hits, 9 unique lore) and Oaths & Vows (1 hit, 1 unique lore). Frost imagery is prominent in lines such as “Please, drink every last drop from the mother chalice.” (lore_id=447464b83f089785) and “Our mother chalice.” (lore_id=4a3a6296ff74bca9). A vow-themed line appears as “And I vow, that when I perfect your form.” (lore_id=3d73082f1ff9e752).",
